## Load-bearing unit invariants (slice 4 reads against these)
- Strict 0..weight (accept; reject <0, >weight, non-integer); re-validated
  against the live component row.
- totalScore = EXACT Σ of component scores (no averaging, rounding, or
  extrapolation).
- letterGrade band edges vs default WAEC: 100→A1, 75→A1, 74→B2, 40→E8,
  39→F9, 0→F9.
- Partial entry (only CA1, exam missing) → total = partial sum, grade
  reflects partial — NOT extrapolated to a full-marks basis. (Most likely
  invariant to get wrong; the one positions rank on.)

